title: Person injured in Lake Worth shooting Sunday night
content:
Autoplay:4 injured in Pahokee, Lake Worth shootingsCONNECTING...
LAKE WORTH, Fla. - One person was injured in a shooting Sunday night in Lake Worth.
The Palm Beach County Sheriff’s Office said the shooting occurred in the area of 7th Avenue North and Federal Highway at 9 p.m.
When deputies arrived at the scene, they found a victim who had been shot.
The condition of the victim is unknown.
